    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Protective envelope-like containers for phonograph records, usually of heavy paper or cardboard and often printed with images and information relating to the record, such as important information about a performance or illustrative material.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
